# Frontend (Next.js)

Follow `docs/UI_GUIDELINES.md` and `docs/CODING_GUIDELINES.md`.

## Must

- App Router; Server Components default; Client Components for interactivity.
- React Query for server data; Zustand for UI/ephemeral state only.
- Loading, empty, error, and skeleton states on async views.
- Role-aware nav; `PermissionGate` for privileged actions.
- Chat: stream + plan + confirmation for medium+ risk tools; citations for RAG.
- Use design tokens / Shadcn variants — no one-off hex sprawl.

## Avoid

Decorative card grids in heroes · business logic in components · raw scattered `fetch` · Inter/purple AI cliché as default brand.
